title: Two hikers missing near North Bend
text:
A search in in progress for two overdue hikers who are missing near North Bend.
King County Search and Rescue got a call around 8:15 p.m. Sunday that the two hikers didn't return home.
Searchers found their car at the Pratt River trailhead.
The overdue hikers have been identified as Jennifer Moran and Elizabeth Edwards Moran. The two are parents of five children.
KIRO 7 has a crew at the scene.
